{"word":"ἐπιφλέγω","slug":"ἐπιφλέγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιφλέγω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to burn up, consume</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>ἐπ. τὴν πόλιν</el> <i>to set fire to</i> it, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to inflame, excite</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be scorching hot</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}